# Auto-HTTPS (Let's Encrypt) for the enjoi API. Requires:
#   - api.enjoimusic.dev resolves to this box (DNS-only / grey cloud on Cloudflare)
#   - ports 80 and 443 open to the internet
# Caddy handles the cert, HTTP->HTTPS redirect, and WebSocket upgrades (/ws).
api.enjoimusic.dev {
	encode zstd gzip
	reverse_proxy api:8723
}
